MaskOri                 Data of 16 participants in a masked orientation
                        discrimination experiment (Hellmann et al.,
                        2023, Exp. 1)
estimateMetaI           Estimate Measures of Metacognition from
                        Information Theory
fitConf                 Fit a static confidence model to data
fitConfModels           Fit several static confidence models to
                        multiple participants
fitMetaDprime           title Compute measures of metacognitive
                        sensitivity (meta-d') and metacognitive
                        efficiency(meta-d'/d') for data from one or
                        several subjects
plotConfModelFit        Plot the prediction of fitted parameters of one
                        model of confidence over the corresponding data
simConf                 Simulate data according to a static model of
                        confidence
